title: Recap: vegan rhetoric vs. vegan reality (why this channel is so different from others).
description: A recap of why this channel is pro-vegan, but critical of the concepts of speciesism, of human-animal equality, and of animal rights as such.  This video is a recap of some of the distinctive approaches to vegan rhetoric that you'll hear on this channel, reflecting a different understanding of vegan reality.
